{"tid":2274304,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【經濟客飯】賭盤比民調可靠 - 曾國平","createTime":"2020-11-06T10:51:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T10:51:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e15345c0dcb781ebfa6d125ff8dd6ab35ed3d8cd","tid":2274304,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T10:51:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201106/APS6JGTGKNHPFIDEBXABSEUNYE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201106%2FAPS6JGTGKNHPFIDEBXABSEUNYE%2F&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9pugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=9ab12bce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201106%2FAPS6JGTGKNHPFIDEBXABSEUNYE%2F&h=5df4ebee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201106/APS6JGTGKNHPFIDEBXABSEUNYE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n【經濟客飯】賭盤比民調可靠 - 曾國平<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/SDG0RR4E7dtmccdAAUSR7p2xtjI=/3000x2000/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UCRLPWLDARH3ZK3XGFF6H7PBZE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSDG0RR4E7dtmccdAAUSR7p2xtjI%3D%2F3000x2000%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUCRLPWLDARH3ZK3XGFF6H7PBZE.jpg&h=1492a22e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■據說今年大選民調在數據處理上作修正，只是碰上疫情的變數，再次讓民調甩轆。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n在本文刊出之時，相信美國大選仍然未有最終結果。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n我不是叫大家以後不信民調，只是提醒大家要有懷疑精神而已。相反，賭盤和預測市場的表現就正路得多。多個後來競爭激烈的州分，選前的賠率都在中間徘徊，就算是傾向拜登，亦非大熱大冷強弱懸殊。<span class=\"orange\">真金白銀的市場，的確能較客觀較即時反映實況。</span><br />\n<br />\n最後分享一點感受。若果你在過去四年只看美國主流傳媒，例如讀《紐約時報》、看CNN頻道、收聽公營電台NPR，那你對特朗普過去各種出位言行必定會有深入了解，同時亦會認為四年過後，不論種族、收入、年齡、性別，都會更討厭這位離經叛道的總統。<br />\n<br />\n結果，特朗普還可大致保住基本盤，支持者還是不離不棄。我見反特朗普的美國朋友在網上發牢騷，說這些人都是冥頑不靈、罔顧現實的笨蛋。這不是健康的態度。我們還是要了解這些特朗普新舊粉絲到底在想甚麼，也要探討主流傳媒到底為何不能全面反映主流意向。<br />\n<br />\n曾國平<br />\n<br />\n美國維珍尼亞理工大學經濟系副教授<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/economics3.0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Feconomics3.0%2F&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9pugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=32cad7af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">fb.com/economics3.0/</a>"}]}